ter = yes\n | hof        = \n | probowl    = \n}}\n{{NFL team draft end}}\n\n===Head coach===\nHead coach [[Ken Whisenhunt]] will be entering his first year of his term with the Cardinals. He was previously the offensive coordinator for the [[Pittsburgh Steelers]].  Whisenhunt signed a contract with the Cardinals on January 14, 2007 after the Cardinals released former head coach [[Dennis Green]].\n\n==Roster==\n{| class=\"toccolours\" style=\"text-align: left;\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"9\" style=\"background-color: #870619; color: white; text-align: center;\"|'''Arizona Cardinals 2007 final roster'''\n|-\n| style=\"font-size: 95%;\" valign=\"top\" | '''Quarterbacks'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">&nbsp;4</span> [[Tim Hasselbeck]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">12</span> [[Tim Rattay]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">13</span> [[Kurt Warner]]\n\n'''Running Backs'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">28</span> [[J. J. Arrington]] KR\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">46</span> ''[[Tim Castille]]'' FB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">32</span> [[Edgerrin James]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">31</span> [[Marcel Shipp]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">45</span> [[Terrelle Smith]] FB\n\n'''Wide Receivers'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">81</span> [[Anquan Boldin]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">15</span> ''[[Steve Breaston]]'' KR/PR\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">11</span> [[Larry Fitzgerald]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">80</span> [[Bryant Johnson]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">87</span> [[Sean Morey (American football)|Sean Morey]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">10</span> [[Jamaica Rector]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">85</span> [[Jerheme Urban]]\n\n'''Tight Ends'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">83</span> [[Troy Bienemann]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">84</span> [[Tim Euhus]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">89</span> ''[[Ben Patrick]]''\n| style=\"width: 25px;\" | \n| style=\"font-size: 95%;\" valign=\"top\" |'''Offensive Linemen'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">61</span> [[Elton Brown]] T/G\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">75</span> ''[[Levi Brown (offensive tackle)|Levi Brown]]'' T\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">69</span> [[Mike Gandy]] T\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">50</span> [[Al Johnson (guard)|Al Johnson]] C\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">76</span> [[Deuce Lutui]] G\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">63</span> ''[[Lyle Sendlein]]'' C\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">73</span> [[Keydrick Vincent]] G\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">74</span> [[Reggie Wells]] G\n\n'''Defensive Linemen'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">91</span> [[Rodney Bailey]] DT\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">78</span> ''[[Alan Branch]]'' DT\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">93</span> [[Chris Cooper (American football)|Chris Cooper]] DT\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">90</span> [[Darnell Dockett]] DT\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">95</span> [[Bo Schobel]] DE\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">94</span> [[Antonio Smith (defensive end)|Antonio Smith]] DE\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">71</span> [[Joe Tafoya]] DE\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">98</span> [[Gabe Watson]] DT\n| style=\"width: 25px;\" |\n| style=\"font-size: 95%;\" valign=\"top\" | '''Linebackers'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">52</span> [[Monty Beisel]] ILB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">51</span> [[Darryl Blackstock]] OLB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">58</span> [[Karlos Dansby]] OLB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">54</span> [[Gerald Hayes]] ILB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">57</