sional, conference opponents were primarily from the [[NFC South]], although they also played [[2007 Washington Redskins season|the Washington Redskins]] from the [[NFC East]], and [[2007 Detroit Lions season|the Detroit Lions]] from the [[NFC North]]. Their non-conference opponents were from the [[AFC North]].\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Week || Date || Opponent || Time ([[Mountain Time Zone|MT]]) || Result || Game site || Record\n|-style=\"background:#ffdddd\"\n! 1\n| September 10, 2007 || at [[2007 San Francisco 49ers season|San Francisco 49ers]] ||8:15 pm||'''L''' 20\u201317 || [[Candlestick Park]] ||0\u20131\n|-style=\"background:#ddffdd\"\n! 2\n| September 16, 2007 || [[2007 Seattle Seahawks season|Seattle Seahawks]] ||2:05 pm||'''W''' 23\u201320 || [[University of Phoenix Stadium]] ||1\u20131\n|-style=\"background:#ffdddd\"\n! 3\n| September 23, 2007 || at [[2007 Baltimore Ravens season|Baltimore Ravens]] ||11:00 am||'''L''' 26\u201323 || [[M&T Bank Stadium]] ||1\u20132\n|-style=\"background:#ddffdd\"\n! 4\n| September 30, 2007 || [[2007 Pittsburgh Steelers season|Pittsburgh Steelers]] ||2:15 pm||'''W''' 21\u201314 || [[University of Phoenix Stadium]] ||2\u20132\n|-style=\"background:#ddffdd\"\n! 5\n| October 7, 2007 || at [[2007 St. Louis Rams season|St. Louis Rams]] ||11:00 am||'''W''' 34\u201331 || [[Edward Jones Dome]] ||3\u20132\n|-style=\"background:#ffdddd\"\n! 6\n| October 14, 2007 || [[2007 Carolina Panthers season|Carolina Panthers]] ||2:05 pm||'''L''' 25\u201310 || [[University of Phoenix Stadium]] ||3\u20133\n|-style=\"background:#ffdddd\"\n! 7\n| October 21, 2007 || at [[2007 Washington Redskins season|Washington Redskins]] ||11:00 am||'''L''' 21\u201319 || [[FedExField]] ||3\u20134\n|-\n! 8\n| colspan=\"6\" align=\"center\" | ''Bye''\n|-style=\"background:#ffdddd\"\n! 9\n| November 4, 2007 || at [[2007 Tampa Bay Buccaneers season|Tampa Bay Buccaneers]] ||11:00 am||'''L''' 17\u201310 || [[Raymond James Stadium]] ||3\u20135\n|-style=\"background:#d